line=134 fonts=F0-14.0 bbox=56.68,752.28,492.42,766.32                                                                              :A language  may  have lost inverse voice and still exhibit inverse morphology.
line=135 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=56.68,731.16,498.76,744.12 iscore=0.08                                                                  :(13)  Consider the Tanoan languages (North Arizona, New Mexico; Klaiman  1993):
line=136 fonts=F0-13.0,F3-13.0 bbox=90.64,716.12,538.64,729.12 iscore=0.13                                                          :      Both Tiwa  and Towa  have an inverse marker but no case, although they have more
line=137 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=90.64,701.16,538.64,714.12 iscore=0.33                                                                  :      than one set of personal affixes, distinguished by whether the nonlocal argument is
line=138 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=90.64,686.16,538.63,699.12 iscore=0.08                                                                  :      singular or plural, animate or inanimate. Tiwa, however, exhibits a further distinction
line=139 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=90.64,671.17,133.84,684.13 iscore=0.08                                                                  :      between
line=140 fonts=F0-10.6,F0-13.0,F1-12.9 bbox=107.68,656.15,364.0,669.13 iscore=0.00                                                  :         ta-   1sg intransitive or transitive inverse (NOM)
line=141 fonts=F0-10.6,F0-13.0,F1-12.9 bbox=107.68,641.15,278.8,654.12 iscore=0.43                                                  :         ti-   1sg transitive direct (SAL)
line=142 fonts=F0-13.0,F3-13.0 bbox=90.64,620.12,538.61,633.12 iscore=0.00                                                          :      Arizona Tewa  (another Tanoan  language) differs: it has no inverse marker, but both
line=143 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=90.64,605.16,538.65,618.12 iscore=0.15                                                                  :      accusative and salience case (moreover, as all Tanoan languages, an oblique marker
line=144 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=90.64,590.16,193.61,603.12 iscore=0.08                                                                  :      in the inverse case).
line=145 fonts=F0-13.0,F2-13.0 bbox=56.68,569.12,506.37,582.12 iscore=0.15                                                          :(14)  Salience case realizes the higher person on the higher argument; Arizona Tewa:
line=146 tag=L span_id=105-8 lang_name=Tewa lang_code=tew fonts=F0-13.0 iscore=0.09 bbox=107.68,554.16,280.86,567.12                :         a. Ne’i  kwiyó     ná:     -tay
line=147 tag=G span_id=105-8 lang_name=Tewa lang_code=tew fonts=F0-10.6,F0-13.0 iscore=1.00 bbox=124.72,539.15,293.8,552.12         :            this  woman     2sg.SAL -know
line=148 tag=T span_id=105-8 lang_name=Tewa lang_code=tew fonts=F0-13.0 iscore=0.75 bbox=124.72,524.16,250.95,537.12                :            ‘You  know this woman’
line=149 tag=L span_id=105-9 lang_name=Tewa lang_code=tew fonts=F0-13.0 iscore=0.17 bbox=107.68,509.16,297.89,522.12                :         b.  Ne’i kwiyó  -di  wó:       -tay
line=150 tag=G span_id=105-9 lang_name=Tewa lang_code=tew fonts=F0-10.5,F0-10.6,F0-13.0 iscore=0.60 bbox=124.72,494.15,310.84,507.12:            this  woman-OBL   2sg.ACC   -know
