line=152 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=56.68,458.16,438.45,471.12 iscore=0.00                                                                  :(15)  Salience case can neither be equated with active, nor with ergative.
line=153 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=90.64,443.16,450.36,456.12 iscore=0.38                                                                  :      a. It cannot be an active marker because there is no intransitive split.
line=154 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=90.64,428.16,538.66,441.12 iscore=0.47                                                                  :      b. It cannot be an ergative case because ergative has to include a 3rd person, but 3sg
line=155 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=107.68,413.16,525.3,426.12 iscore=0.19                                                                  :         is lacking in Tewa. Moreover, Tiwa gives evidence that this case starts with 1sg.
line=156 fonts=F1-13.0 bbox=90.64,398.24,443.8,411.2 iscore=0.07                                                                    :      direct setting          inverse setting             intransitives
line=157 fonts=F0-10.6,F0-13.0,F4-13.0 bbox=90.64,382.28,443.32,395.29 iscore=0.50                                                  :      λy    λx  VERB(x,y)     λy    λx   VERB(x,y)        λx VERB(x)
line=158 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=90.64,366.32,405.28,379.32 iscore=0.50                                                                  :      +hr   +lr               +hr   +lr                 −hr,−lr
line=159 fonts=F0-13.0 bbox=93.88,351.36,389.44,364.32 iscore=0.00                                                                  :       3     1                  1     3                   1
